      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UNACCEPTABLE ROB (1) is boxed nicely on the inside. Latest effort finished 4th over 390m at this track beaten 7 lengths (22.25) behind Borneo Traveler in a Grade 5 on May 15. Looks suited and should go close. DAYTONA SUNSET (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (18.98) at Q Straight behind Flagman Franky in a Grade 5. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Can feature again. REDMAN JOHNNY (4) doesn't win out of turn but looks close to breaking through. Has hit the frame at his last three runs, the latest finishing second (22.05) at this track. Expecting another good run. MONTY ZOOMER (3) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
